'''Terminus Fourteen Access Corridor''' was a corridor on the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|first Death Star]]. It was the location where [[Master chief petty officer]] [[Tenn Graneet]] brushed by [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] and nearly tugged on the [[Sith Lord/Legends|Sith Lord's]] cape.

